& [HierarchicalAgentSwarmSpecification] is the working canonical specification for a Shaliach-advised, Manager-governed, Director-negotiated, Programmer-implemented local coding agent
  @ [source_document] specifications/source/2026-05-29_hierarchical_agent_swarm_source.sop
