  + [authority_scope] is architecture, orchestration, model tiering, flowchart negotiation, implementation slicing, programmer review, and local model hosting for NegotiatedCodingAgent
  + [non_authority_scope] is final security sandbox policy, final model inventory, production deployment, billing, cloud inference, and unrelated TheBrain projects
